1
00:00:00,120 --> 00:00:01,620
Thực hành ElastiCache (Redis).

2
00:00:01,620 --> 00:00:03,030
Chọn Redis (cũng có Memcached).

3
00:00:03,030 --> 00:00:04,500
Tùy chọn:

4
00:00:04,500 --> 00:00:07,590
- Serverless: tự scale, không quản lý server (đắt hơn, dễ vận hành).

5
00:00:07,590 --> 00:00:11,370
- Tự thiết kế: dễ hiểu kiến trúc — chọn thiết kế thủ công.

6
00:00:11,370 --> 00:00:12,510
Phương thức tạo: Easy create (prod/dev/test)

7
00:00:12,510 --> 00:00:14,370
hoặc cấu hình đầy đủ.

8
00:00:14,370 --> 00:00:16,290
Cluster mode: Disabled (1 shard: 1 primary, ≤5 replica).

9
00:00:16,290 --> 00:00:18,540
Muốn nhiều shard -> bật cluster mode.

10
00:00:18,540 --> 00:00:20,520
Đặt tên: DemoCluster. Location: AWS Cloud

11
00:00:20,520 --> 00:00:21,750
(có thể on‑prem qua AWS Outposts).

12
00:00:21,750 --> 00:00:24,660
Multi‑AZ (HA + failover): tắt để giảm phí (demo).

13
00:00:24,660 --> 00:00:27,150
Engine version/port/parameter group: giữ mặc định.

14
00:00:27,150 --> 00:00:28,770
Node type: chọn micro (t2/t3 free tier).

15
00:00:28,770 --> 00:00:30,090
Replica count: 0 (demo, tiết kiệm phí).

16
00:00:30,090 --> 00:00:32,640
Subnet group: tạo mới (chọn VPC + subnets).

17
00:00:32,640 --> 00:00:35,940
AZ placement: bỏ qua nếu không Multi‑AZ.

18
00:00:35,940 --> 00:00:39,150
Encryption: at rest (KMS key) / in transit (TLS) — nếu bật

19
00:00:39,150 --> 00:00:41,220
thì có Access Control: Redis AUTH (token) hoặc User Group ACL.

20
00:00:41,220 --> 00:00:44,580
Networking/Security: SG, preferred AZ, maintenance window,

21
00:00:44,580 --> 00:00:46,650
CloudWatch Logs (slowlog/engine logs), tags.

22
00:00:46,650 --> 00:00:48,960
Review và Create cluster.

23
00:00:48,960 --> 00:00:51,780
Sau khi tạo: dùng Primary endpoint (và Reader endpoint nếu có)

24
00:00:51,780 --> 00:00:55,020
trong code ứng dụng để kết nối Redis.

25
00:00:55,020 --> 00:00:57,030
Từ console: xem nodes, metrics, logs, network, security,…

26
00:00:57,030 --> 00:05:00,150
Cuối cùng: Action -> Delete cluster (không cần backup) để tránh phí.

